			<div class="content" id="post-content-1015418">
									

<p>Hrm, this one is….interesting. Definitely a neat concept, but it needs a lot of work in my opinion.</p>
<p>First off, your first interview log doesn't add very much, while the second adds nothing at all. Interview logs are meant to be used to demonstrate details that cannot be adequately conveyed through the standard report format. Your second one just repeats exactly what the report says, almost word for word. You also need to fix the format of the interview logs, they are kind of awkward.</p>
<p>But yeah, besides all that, I feel like this SCP just needs some oomph to it. Right now it's just "okay, he looks funny. So?" It needs some kind of hook, or catch, something to make it work. Take 682 for example: on it's own, an unkillable lizard just isn't that interesting. Add in a desire to massacre humanity, and you have something worth fearing. That being said, don't make this one "just kills everything" or "makes you go crazy", those have been overdone.</p>
<p>Withholding vote pending an update or lack thereof.</p>
<p>So yeah, there's my two cents. Good luck!</p>
<p>EDIT: Just saw that you fixed the interview log format. Well done.</p>

